            <div id="restofstory2" class="more">
                <span id="ChapterParagraphTwo">
                    We were totally surprised. But we said, “Of course. Yes, we will serve.” It was something that you just do. To us it was like we had been called to serve in a ward. It was the same thing. We were asked to do something, and we set about to do it. <br /><br />

                    We got our affairs in order. We had someone in the family that was able to come and manage the apartments, and we had some family move into our home and take care of it. We knew that the Lord would take care of things that needed to be done, so we just did it. We accepted the call and said, “Yes. We’ll go.”
 
